com.vernalis.knime.mmp

Class BondIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.knime.mmp.BondIdentifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<BondIdentifier>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>

    public class BondIdentifier
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<BondIdentifier>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>
    A class to hold the start and end atom IDs together, along with the bond ID at time of creation. The object is iterable, iterating through the integer atom IDs in the order start, end
    Author:
    s.roughley <knime@vernalis.com>
